show.title: The Wake Up Call

title: Obamacare: An Economic Catastrophe
content:
Full account of the problems surrounding the worst launch of a website in history. A media-inspired cover-up. Massive premium increases.
Doctors abandoning patients from the ACA in droves.
Comparisons with other countries.
The financial minefield being prepared by a Congress of millionaires.
The deficit is not going down.
Learn about ‘the trick’.
A couple of quick comments on the stock market.
More grim economic statistics.
Ramifications of the recent, alarming fall in consumer confidence.
Comment from whistleblower, William Binney, about the current spying program at the NSA.
